<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٥٩:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {إِنَّا لَمَّا طَغَى الْمَاءُ حَمَلْنَاكُمْ فِي الْجَارِيَةِ <span class="c2">(١١)</span> لِنَجْعَلَهَا لَكُمْ تَذْكِرَةً وَتَعِيَهَا أُذُنٌ وَاعِيَةٌ (١٢} <span class="c4">[الحاقة: ١١، ١٢]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> <span class="c3">{طَغَى}</span>: <span class="c1">" كَثُرَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَيُقَالُ:</span> طَغَتْ عَلَى الخَزَّانِ , كَمَا طَغَى المَاءُ عَلَى قَوْمِ نُوحٍ "<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٩ص١٦٠:</span> قَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ: <span class="c3">{وَتَعِيَهَا}</span>: <span class="c2">«تَحْفَظُهَا»</span>،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{وَاعِيَةٌ}</span>: <span class="c2">«حَافِظَةٌ»</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>